   "description": "This host's WireGuard public key on the wg-mesh private-plane fabric, derived (not stored) from the Server UUID. Shown for legibility; the controller recomputes it from atlas.networking.derive_host_wireguard_keypair. The private key is injected at bootstrap and never stored.",
