   "fieldtype": "Data",
   "label": "WireGuard Public Key",
   "read_only": 1
  },
  {
   "description": "This host's own fdaa:0:0:<idx>::1 endpoint on the mesh bus (the infra /48), used for host-to-host transport (migration NBD, snapshot replication, image fan-out) inside the tunnel. Derived from the Server UUID; shown for legibility.",
